{
  "stem": "6195.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were always, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] how shall I say, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] riots.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had to call an ambulance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Jewish students were injured.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, and they used to call out, out with the Jews, in with Jewesses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They liked the Jewish girls, because they were attractive and clever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That doesn't go to say that the non-Jewish were not clever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But that was the general idea, that the Jews are clever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who, I?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I went to a Hebrew high school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was a, a, a dilemma.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I did want to study, at first, medicine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Speaking of medicine, I had an uncle who was a very Orthodox Jew and was a professor in medicine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See, you can combine things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was so interested in it that I wanted to study medicine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "However, there were two reasons for which I didn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First of all, in the year that I was eligible to go to university, Jews were not admitted anymore to the faculty.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a numerus nullus for Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Secondly, I was very interested in languages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was a separate school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But my father didn't subscribe to any of it, because [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there were reasons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He had his own reasons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I would mix with the non-Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I may fell in love with a Jew-- non-Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I would have to go on Saturday to the library, or wherever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was not [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I wasn't quite happy about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But in those days, we didn't rebel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's what parents said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was another-- it was a-- like a school that taught you the same.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
